WEBVTT

00:07:59.759 --> 00:08:01.641
and drinkable water.

00:08:02.280 --> 00:08:06.750
It's a gift that millions
and millions in the world

00:08:06.774 --> 00:08:08.738
will never experience.

00:08:09.837 --> 00:08:14.977
So these are just a few
of an enormous number of gifts

00:08:15.001 --> 00:08:16.830
to which we can open your heart.

00:08:18.513 --> 00:08:21.784
And so I wish you
that you will open your heart

00:08:21.808 --> 00:08:24.751
to all these blessings,

00:08:24.775 --> 00:08:27.191
and let them flow through you,

00:08:28.270 --> 00:08:31.608
that everyone whom you
will meet on this day